-- Blackstone to Invest as Much as $3 Billion in India by 2015, Mint Reports
-- Anoop Agrawal
-- 2010-06-22T01:34:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-22/blackstone-to-invest-as-much-as-3-billion-in-india-by-2015-mint-reports.html

          
          
             Blackstone Group LP plans to invest
as much as $3 billion over the next five years in India, the
Mint newspaper reported, citing Akhil Gupta, chairman and
managing director of the Indian unit.  
